</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Erwirdig<ex>en</ex></expan> und lieben
                        <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch fürbracht sey, daz
                        Jacob <expan>Prünst<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>, den <expan cert="unknown">H.</expan> Lewpolt,
                        zu fenknuss bracht hab etc., das haben wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und wie wol
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Jacob <expan>Prünst<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> niht ist, doch umb
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> und
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen, <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wir in besandt und sein rede <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> gehöret; der hat
                        uns geantwurt, daz er den <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> niht <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>sund<ex>er</ex></expan> von <add>seinr notdurft
                                    <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> mit recht</add> bey uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>potten</expan> und mit
                                <expan>frewntliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>zugesproche<ex>n</ex></expan> hab, also stee die sache zwischen in in
                        recht. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erwirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
